OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAfghanistan: Top UK        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fofficial regrets holiday as
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcountry fell to Taliban    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Foreign Office's most senior civil 
OL,6, servant said he regrets continuing his 
OL,7, summer holiday while Afghanistan fell  
OL,8, to the Taliban.                        
OL,10,FSir Philip Barton remained on holiday  
OL,11,Ffor 11 days after the Taliban seized   
OL,12,FKabul, returning the day before the UK 
OL,13,Fended its evacuation of civilians.     
OL,15,FIt comes after a whistleblower said the
OL,16,FUK evacuation had been chaotic and     
OL,17,Fdysfunctional.                         
OL,19,FSir Philip told MPs his presence would 
OL,20,Fnot have led to more people evacuated. 
